### Layer 1 closure check

Layer 1 is closed-for-work when all of:

- [ ] Every K has all 7 fields filled (no `TBD`)
- [ ] Every K passes operational filter Conditions 0-3
  (`references/rd/core_technologies.md`)
- [ ] Lifecycle of every K is explicitly assigned (no defaults)
- [ ] Every K has literature link OR `(none, novel)` justified
- [ ] Cross-K dependencies (if any) noted in `decisions.md`

Layer 1 closure unlocks Section 2 work. Adding a new K after closure
requires a deviation entry in `decisions.md`.

