### Status legend

- `active`: currently being worked on
- `matured`: target_TRL hit, kill un-fired, A4+ analysis recorded
- `blocked`: named dependency unresolved
- `split`: decomposed into 2+ children (parent stays for traceability)
- `merged`: absorbed into another capability
- `stale`: no longer relevant after scope change
- `parked`: deferred with named unblock condition
- `killed`: kill criterion fired with A4+ evidence

